ActCanadian Wheat Board (Interim Operations) Act
SubjectCanadian Wheat Board ** Acquisition of Property **
PrecisOrder authorizing the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to acquire real property in the form of a parcel of land held by Raymond Joseph Louis Philippe and Claudette Antoinette Philippe, located near St. Adolphe in the parish of Sainte Agathe, Manitoba.
